name: Outreach to chonky
description: Hi, chonky, I am father of an MAS patient. I have recently put my NFT project online to fund for my daughter's medical expense and a local MAS organization. But since I am nobody, my project is not noticed at all. The project site is http://mas-awareness.top and my twitter is https://x.com/Ric_Li_C. Please support by getting NFT at 0.09 BNB each or just spreading the word to let more people know. Thank you.
